{
  "id": "cli/new",
  "title": "ng new",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/new\", \"name\": \"new\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-new\">ng new<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/new#ng-new\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    \n    <p translation-origin=\"off\">Creates a new workspace and an initial Angular app.</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">new</span> &#x3C;<var>name</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">n</span> &#x3C;<var>name</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">Arguments</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Argument</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code>name</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">The name of the workspace.</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">Options</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Option</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--collection=<var>collection</var></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-c=<var>collection</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Schematics collection to use.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--commit=<span class=\"cli-default\">true</span>|<span>false</span>\n--<span class=\"cli-default\">commit</span>|--<span>noCommit</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Initial repository commit information.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--createApplication=<span class=\"cli-default\">true</span>|<span>false</span>\n--<span class=\"cli-default\">createApplication</span>|--<span>noCreateApplication</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Flag to toggle creation of an application in the new workspace.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--defaults=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>defaults</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noDefaults</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">When true, disables interactive input prompts for options with a default.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--directory=<var>directory</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">The directory name to create the workspace in.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--dryRun=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>dryRun</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noDryRun</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-d=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>d</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noD</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">When true, run through and report activity without writing out results.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--experimentalIvy=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>experimentalIvy</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noExperimentalIvy</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">EXPERIMENTAL: Specifies whether to create a new application which uses the Ivy rendering engine.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--force=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>force</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noForce</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-f=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>f</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noF</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">When true, force overwriting of existing files.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--<span>help</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noHelp</span></code>\n        \n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--help=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>|<span><a href=\"api/common/JsonPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">json</a></span>|<span>JSON</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Shows a help message for this command in the console.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--inlineStyle=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>inlineStyle</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noInlineStyle</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-s=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>s</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noS</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Specifies if the style will be in the ts file.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--inlineTemplate=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>inlineTemplate</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noInlineTemplate</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-t=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>t</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noT</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Specifies if the template will be in the ts file.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--interactive=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>interactive</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noInteractive</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">When false, disables interactive input prompts.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--minimal=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>minimal</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noMinimal</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Create a barebones project without any testing frameworks</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--newProjectRoot=<var>newProjectRoot</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">The path where new projects will be created.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--prefix=<var>prefix</var></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-p=<var>prefix</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">The prefix to apply to generated selectors.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--routing=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>routing</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noRouting</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Generates a routing module.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--skipGit=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>skipGit</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noSkipGit</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-g=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>g</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noG</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Skip initializing a git repository.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--skipInstall=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>skipInstall</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noSkipInstall</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Skip installing dependency packages.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--skipTests=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>skipTests</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noSkipTests</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-S=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>S</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noS</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Skip creating spec files.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--style=<var>style</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">The file extension to be used for style files.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--verbose=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>verbose</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noVerbose</span></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-v=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n-<span>v</span>|-<span class=\"cli-default\">noV</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Adds more details to output logging.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--viewEncapsulation=<span><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\" class=\"code-anchor\">Emulated</a></span>|<span><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Native\" class=\"code-anchor\">Native</a></span>|<span><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\" class=\"code-anchor\">None</a></span>|<span>ShadowDom</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Specifies the view encapsulation strategy.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n    <p translation-origin=\"off\">Creates and initializes a new Angular app that is the default project for a new workspace.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Provides interactive prompts for optional configuration, such as adding routing support.\nAll prompts can safely be allowed to default.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The new workspace folder is given the specified project name, and contains configuration files at the top level. </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The new app files are placed in the <code>src/</code> subfolder. A corresponding end-to-end test app is placed in the <code>e2e/</code> subfolder.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The new app's configuration appears in the <code>projects</code> section of the <code>angular.json</code> workspace configuration file, under its project name.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/router\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/JsonPipe\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Native\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#None\n - cli\n - cli/new#ng-new\n-->"
}